This '''Member of the Thirteen''' is an unnamed recurring character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by guest star [[Slavko Juraga]] and debuts in &quot;[[Garden of Bones]].&quot; He is killed by [[Pyat Pree]] when [[Xaro Xhoan Daxos]] proclaims himself King of [[Qarth]].

sections.Biography:
===Background===
He is a member of [[the Thirteen]], the rulers of [[Qarth]].

===[[Season 2]]===
He receives [[Daenerys Targaryen]] outside the gates of the city with the rest of [[the Thirteen]]. They refuse to admit her without seeing her [[dragons]]. She is defiant and is eventually admitted under the protection of [[Xaro Xhoan Daxos]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Garden of Bones]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

He's present at a gathering of Qartheen dignataries attended by Daenerys, accompanied by [[Unsullied|her protectors]] and Xaro Xhoan Daxos.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Ghost of Harrenhal]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

He's present at a session of the Thirteen in which Daenerys accuses the [[Spice King]] of stealing her dragons. He's murdered by one of the doubles of [[Pyat Pree]] along with the rest of the Qartheen merchant lords after the [[warlock]] reveals he stole the dragons and that his in league with Xaro Xhoan Daxos to make him [[King of Qarth]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[A Man Without Honor]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
